==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Somnambulist
<hw>Som*nam"bu*list</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who
is subject to somnambulism; one who walks in his sleep; a sleepwalker; a
noctambulist.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> somnambulator.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Somnambulistic</ent>⟦br⟧
